                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT7287PrBaryaSusenyos">Prayer against Bāryā, Legewon and various demons and diseases</title>
                            <note>Magic prayer against the pain of Bāryā and Legewon, ʿaynat, Maggāññā, pleurisy, Tayāž, ʾƎǧa sabʾ, budā, blacksmiths,
                                contagious disease, and malarial fever, containing an enforcement referring to the 
                                <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1763Legend">legend of Susǝnyos</ref>.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ 
                                ሕማመ<supplied resp="PRS8999Strelcyn" reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ወዓይነት፡ መገኛ፡ ወጉሥምት፡ ተያዥ፡ 
                                ወእጀሰብእ፡ ቡዳ፡ ወጠቢብ፡ ፌራ፡ ወንዳድ፡ በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ነባቢ፡ ወተናጋሪ፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ 
                                <persName ref="PRS9038Susenyos">ሱስንዮስ፡</persName></incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <title type="complete" ref="LIT4697MagicPr"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ 
                                ማዕሰሮሙ<supplied resp="PRS8999Strelcyn" reason="omitted">፡</supplied>
                                ለአጋንንት<supplied resp="PRS8999Strelcyn" reason="omitted">።</supplied>
                                ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ሰዳዴ፡ ሰይጣናት፡ ፋኑኤል፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ እምጽርሑ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
